        <h1>If God Controls Everything, How Can He Blame Us?</h1>
        <p>You just asked the most natural question in the world—and Paul anticipated it 2,000 years ago. Scripture teaches that God predetermines all things and holds us fully responsible. That tension isn't a flaw in the truth; it's the center of the biblical worldview.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="section-nav">
